<Layout>
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="text-gold">The Life of Umesh Chandra</h1>
      <p>This section of the website is dedicated to the life of Mr. Umesh Chandra, from his childhood to his lasting legacy. Explore the different stages of his life through the following sections:</p>
      
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title text-gold">Childhood</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Learn about the early years of Mr. Umesh Chandra's life, his upbringing, and the values that shaped him.</p>
              <a href="/life/childhood" class="btn btn-primary">Read More</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title text-gold">Schooling & University</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Discover his academic journey, from his school days to his time at the university, and the foundation it laid for his future.</p>
              <a href="/life/schooling-university" class="btn btn-primary">Read More</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title text-gold">IPS Journey</h5>
